<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Kasy Ride</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            /* background: white; */
            background-image: url('https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/04/99/56/30/240_F_499563059_GGQxzylCFmlUlL1jr5rVrbYE9yk9vkmp.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            border: 1px solid#ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            clear: both;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .feature {
            width: 30%;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

            .feature h3 {
                margin-top: 10px;
                color: #0077cc;
            }

        .cta-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

            .cta-buttons a {
                padding: 12px 20px;
                margin: 10px;
                background-color: #0077cc;
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: 1rem;
                border-radius: 5px;
            }

                .cta-buttons a:hover {
                    background-color: #005fa3;
                }

       
    </style>
</head>
<body>
            <header>
                <h1>Welcome to Your Kasy Ride</h1>
                <p>Your Ride, Your Way.</p>
                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS02qPnvJZZtWoCfpC1S7quJUEsSJxehJQmOQ&s" alt="logo" width="100" height="100" />
            </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section>
            <h2>Get Where You Need to Be – Fast, Safe, and Reliable</h2>
            <p>Whether it's a quick trip across town or a long journey ahead, we're here to make sure your ride is as smooth and comfortable as possible.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Affordable Rates</h3>
                <p>Transparent pricing with no hidden fees. Pay only what you see.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Fast & Reliable</h3>
                <p>Get a ride in minutes, with drivers nearby and real-time tracking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Safe & Secure</h3>
                <p>Track your ride and share your journey with loved ones for added security.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-buttons">
            <h2>Ready to Ride?</h2>
            <p>Choose your ride and start your journey with just a few taps.</p>
            <a href="#">Download for iOS</a>
            <a href="#">Download for Android</a>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>